Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.68,0:00:07.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那麼請您在回收同意書上籤名
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.87,0:00:13.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}要和米拉貝爾離別什麼的 會變的寂寞呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.73,0:00:15.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}這孩子是小熊小阿
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.65,0:00:16.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你好～
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.09,0:00:17.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.08,0:00:21.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那麼關於米拉貝爾的回收
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.13,0:00:25.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}持有者的您有三個方案可選擇
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.11,0:00:28.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}第一是 重新購買的折扣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.65,0:00:32.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}第二是 舊換新來得到定價的三成現金回饋
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.30,0:00:36.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}第三是 植入新的OS在米拉貝爾的身體中
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.44,0:00:39.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}也就是說 換上新的人格繼續使用
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.94,0:00:41.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}煩請您植入新的OS了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.42,0:00:48.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那個… 人格和記憶都會消失喔
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.97,0:00:50.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那樣也沒關係嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.68,0:00:53.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯 以前就是這樣做的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.18,0:00:55.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}以前就是 是指…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.06,0:01:00.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}即使更換了靈魂我也依然把她當作同一個人對待
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.33,0:01:25.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}記憶？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.61,0:01:26.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.61,0:01:28.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}更換了OS之後的吉芙提爾
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.74,0:01:33.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}有沒有可能在某種情況下恢復了以前的記憶呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.00,0:01:35.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.51,0:01:37.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}沒有沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.04,0:01:39.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}非常可惜
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.48,0:01:41.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}沒有呢 從來沒有先例
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.39,0:01:43.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}怎麼可能有呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.10,0:01:46.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你到處亂晃就是為了問這個嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.26,0:01:49.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}所以我才受不了外行人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.52,0:01:53.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}唉 滿還是一如既往的咄咄逼人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.45,0:01:54.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}吉芙提爾的這種情況
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.83,0:01:57.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}和人類喪失記憶是完全不同的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.22,0:02:01.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}內在被完全替換成全新的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.55,0:02:02.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}已經是不同的東西了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.03,0:02:03.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}完完全全的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.41,0:02:05.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}這點上可不要搞錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.51,0:02:10.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}所以就可以認為無可奈何而果斷接受嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.15,0:02:14.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}讓人空有期望白白等待才更痛苦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.85,0:02:19.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嘛 我也能夠理解你的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.48,0:02:24.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我在來這裡之前也曾經想過相同的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.98,0:02:26.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}滿
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.95,0:02:30.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}所以必須想辦法讓自己去接受這個事實
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.85,0:02:33.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}這也是沒有辦法的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.64,0:02:41.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}司 艾拉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.09,0:02:47.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}明天第三終端服務派遣的執行者會到這裡來
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.69,0:02:48.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}第三？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.89,0:02:53.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}他們負責的所有者和回收對象聽說躲起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.74,0:02:56.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}有情報說他們潛伏在我們的負責區域內
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.56,0:02:57.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}所以就派人來搜索了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.58,0:02:59.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}突然提出這個要求是在抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.91,0:03:01.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但是希望你們可以去支援她
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.39,0:03:03.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好的 我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.41,0:03:05.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}司
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.69,0:03:09.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}交給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.91,0:03:13.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你們就是司和艾拉嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.90,0:03:17.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我是第三終端服務的安迪
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.51,0:03:18.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}請多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.65,0:03:19.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}彼此彼此
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.12,0:03:23.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}話說回來 安迪的搭檔呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.62,0:03:24.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}沒有來呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.06,0:03:25.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.72,0:03:28.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}出差要執行者一個人去才是基本政策吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.72,0:03:30.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}第一終端服務不是這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.49,0:03:31.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不知道…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.87,0:03:33.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我沒出差過
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.61,0:03:37.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}特地派兩個人出來效率很低不是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.37,0:03:42.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}在出差地會準備像你們這樣的支援
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.24,0:03:43.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}也不會有什麼困擾
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.53,0:03:44.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.82,0:03:47.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但是如果艾拉去出差的話
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.40,0:03:49.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我肯定也會跟去的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.92,0:03:53.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}出差什麼的我一個人也是可以的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.53,0:03:54.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}咦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.96,0:03:58.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我可以的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.28,0:04:01.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不 不是那個意思
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.94,0:04:02.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你誤會了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.78,0:04:04.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}錯誤 沒有聽清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.49,0:04:06.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.25,0:04:09.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你們兩個真是奇怪的組合呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.13,0:04:11.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}小司
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.49,0:04:16.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}奧利維拉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.44,0:04:17.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.01,0:04:18.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.23,0:04:21.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}難以置信
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.19,0:04:25.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我的知心好友啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.93,0:04:28.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\blur2}那個時候…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.79,0:04:29.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}繪瑠小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.08,0:04:33.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你在摸哪裡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.29,0:04:38.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}沒想到你居然會反擊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.26,0:04:39.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真是嚇到我了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.44,0:04:42.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}明明以前不管摸多久都不會反抗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.55,0:04:45.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不過這樣也有這樣的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.42,0:04:49.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}話說…兩位是認識的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.76,0:04:50.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.63,0:04:54.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我們可是一同度過了青春時代的好友
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.89,0:04:56.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你在說什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.45,0:05:00.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我們不是第一次見面嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.00,0:05:01.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}咦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.07,0:05:04.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}繪瑠小姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.44,0:05:09.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}抱歉你跟我朋友長得太像了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.50,0:05:10.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不小心認錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.87,0:05:13.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我還真是冒失呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.62,0:05:18.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那我先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.12,0:05:21.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}第一終端服務這邊的人都好奇怪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.30,0:05:29.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}這樣啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.18,0:05:31.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}已經消失了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.85,0:05:32.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}記憶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.84,0:05:45.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}等下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.50,0:05:53.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}艾拉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.71,0:05:54.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.47,0:05:59.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}趁現在
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.25,0:06:00.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}到此為止了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.16,0:06:05.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你們能就此放棄了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.65,0:06:18.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}請在這裡簽字
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.09,0:06:21.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}拜託 放過他吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.41,0:06:24.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我不想離開德瑞克
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.31,0:06:25.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我愛他
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.36,0:06:27.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}這樣不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.82,0:06:31.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那至少到期限為止讓我和他在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.31,0:06:35.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}一週左右的話沒問題的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.30,0:06:36.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那也不行
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.99,0:06:39.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你們又會逃跑的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.07,0:06:40.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}怎麼這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.62,0:06:47.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}德瑞克！ 德瑞克！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.44,0:06:50.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}吶 安迪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.28,0:07:07.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真是幫大忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.64,0:07:11.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}托你們的福 回收的進程比計劃快了很多
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.60,0:07:15.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯？ 你怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.81,0:07:18.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}有必要那麼強硬嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.47,0:07:20.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你說什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.98,0:07:25.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那樣的話 和持有者引發矛盾也不足為奇吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.02,0:07:28.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我已經習慣了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.30,0:07:31.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}銷毀回憶是我們的工作啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.12,0:07:36.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}安迪並沒有錯哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.67,0:07:38.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊 謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.88,0:07:42.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}倒不如說終端服務一般都是這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.48,0:07:44.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.28,0:07:47.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}只有我們不一樣哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.59,0:07:51.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}還要照顧持有者和回收對象的心理感受什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.01,0:07:55.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}再說這還是香月三年前開始使用的做法
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.92,0:07:56.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.29,0:08:00.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就因為這個課長還經常被總部叫過去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.37,0:08:02.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}因為經費花得太多被發牢騷
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.45,0:08:09.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}咦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.82,0:08:16.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}難道你在等我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.77,0:08:18.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.82,0:08:23.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我剛才去找康孝先生請教了一下關於今天的事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.50,0:08:24.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我也…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.58,0:08:24.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.13,0:08:29.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我也想參與你請教的問題
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.63,0:08:34.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯 那下次就和艾拉聊聊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.76,0:08:41.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真的長得一模一樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.84,0:08:43.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊 好的好的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.34,0:08:46.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那 今天就這樣 再見啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.43,0:08:51.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}剛才是安迪嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.38,0:08:54.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊…嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.41,0:08:56.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}之前的事想道個歉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.32,0:08:57.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就打電話給她了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.63,0:09:01.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}然後就完全被喜歡上了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.59,0:09:03.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}受歡迎的女性真不好過呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.61,0:09:09.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}話說 聽你們對話好像你之前就認識安迪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.58,0:09:10.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.19,0:09:14.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我們以前是鄰居
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.95,0:09:17.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}她當時叫奧莉維亞
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.56,0:09:19.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}當時？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.67,0:09:20.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你看
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.52,0:09:26.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}這真的是安迪嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.37,0:09:29.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}感覺給人印象不一樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.72,0:09:34.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}奧莉維亞在幾年前被回收了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.51,0:09:38.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}難道是…更換了OS嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.83,0:09:39.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.60,0:09:46.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你看啊 終端服務不是總說要削減經費嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.79,0:09:50.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}所以本來應該被銷毀的奧莉維亞
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.13,0:09:51.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就被重新利用了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.02,0:09:57.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}安迪還有身為奧莉維亞那時候的記憶嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.17,0:10:02.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}沒想到還能以這種形式再見面
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.45,0:10:06.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}竟然還能揉到那胸
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.63,0:10:09.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}奧莉維亞的 雖然現在是安迪
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.34,0:10:11.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}以前可是經常讓我揉的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.53,0:10:13.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}正確的說是我強行去揉的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.80,0:10:13.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}{\an8}這人已經沒救了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.22,0:10:15.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.99,0:10:27.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那已經不是奧莉維亞了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.42,0:10:30.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}繪瑠小姐已經不在意了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.58,0:10:33.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}這種事不值得在意嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.70,0:10:38.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}大概是這樣的吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.78,0:10:48.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}點心送到了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.67,0:10:50.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}哦 誰送的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.53,0:10:53.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}第三終端服務的課長送來的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.32,0:10:55.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.22,0:10:57.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}小艾拉 沏茶麻煩你了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.60,0:11:02.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}幾天前來的安迪幹活真是俐落呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.69,0:11:03.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}給人一種「刷刷」地搞定工作
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.77,0:11:06.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}「嗖」地就回來了的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.33,0:11:09.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗚哇 這是在說我們不中用嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.95,0:11:12.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不不 並不是那個意思哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.85,0:11:13.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}這可難說
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.36,0:11:16.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}小司
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.08,0:11:22.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}請幫幫我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.74,0:11:29.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我不小心和安迪說了我老家嘉年華的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.13,0:11:33.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}然後她非要我帶她去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.27,0:11:34.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}喔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.13,0:11:37.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但那個嘉年華是今晚啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.41,0:11:40.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}所以司司 拜託和我一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.74,0:11:42.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}為什麼我要去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.41,0:11:44.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你們兩個人好好玩一下不就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.43,0:11:45.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不行不行不行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.08,0:11:46.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.01,0:11:51.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}因為那裡全是和奧莉維亞在一起的回憶啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.90,0:11:54.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}和安迪一起去的話
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.16,0:11:56.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}太折磨人了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.14,0:11:58.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}畢竟長得一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.37,0:12:01.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}繪瑠小姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.44,0:12:05.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}小司～ 跟我一起來啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.63,0:12:09.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就當作幫我一個忙 拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.57,0:12:12.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}{\an8}呃 不 等等 啊啊 別抱這麼緊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.89,0:12:16.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那兩個人在偷偷摸摸幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.44,0:12:17.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}艾拉 你有在聽嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.36,0:12:19.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你真的很在意呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.83,0:12:23.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}連搭檔都不告訴肯定有問題不是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.31,0:12:26.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我沒有特別在意
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.70,0:12:28.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是喔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.79,0:12:33.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你很在意對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.82,0:12:38.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那個…只是舉例而已
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.71,0:12:41.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}帶安迪去嘉年華的話
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.20,0:12:49.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}以此為契機奧莉維亞的記憶可能會回來一些些… 有可能嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.96,0:12:53.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你在思考著艾拉拉的事情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.72,0:12:55.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}怎麼說呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.33,0:13:00.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}無論我說什麼你都不會那麼簡單就認同的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.10,0:13:06.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}所以說沒關係 司司就盡情的利用我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.70,0:13:07.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}利用是指…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.49,0:13:14.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}今晚一起去吧 然後在那邊用自己的雙眼去確認就行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.20,0:13:17.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我也要去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.75,0:13:19.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不用勉強也沒關係喔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.17,0:13:22.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我是司的夥伴
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.07,0:13:25.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}順帶一提 安迪也會去的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.14,0:13:26.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.99,0:13:29.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}還有 繪瑠小姐也會跟著去唷
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.00,0:13:31.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.08,0:13:34.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯 那就這樣決定了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.60,0:13:38.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}最後還會放煙火 很熱鬧的唷
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.78,0:13:42.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我從來都沒實際看過煙火呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.50,0:13:43.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}沒看過嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.87,0:13:47.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}聲音很大 你一定會嚇一跳的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.19,0:13:49.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}聲音…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.11,0:13:54.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}把耳朵塞起來比較好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.32,0:13:56.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}呃 不 不用塞起來也沒關係…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.55,0:13:57.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那這樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.79,0:13:59.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}呃 所以說沒關係啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.57,0:14:06.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嘿 還真多人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.94,0:14:09.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}艾拉拉超可愛 超可愛的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.43,0:14:16.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}總感覺好興奮呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.57,0:14:21.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}很少有機會來這種地方呢 成為繪瑠的朋友真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.39,0:14:24.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那就到處逛逛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.89,0:14:36.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}司… 司！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.56,0:14:44.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}都只有我和繪瑠嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.96,0:14:46.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}也應該幫艾拉照幾張呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.11,0:14:49.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊 是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.35,0:14:51.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}安迪 我們喝點什麼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.74,0:14:53.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好啊 有些什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.48,0:14:57.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}艾拉 要看嗎 就像好姐妹一樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.83,0:15:04.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}呃 要不艾拉也來照一張吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.29,0:15:10.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}錯誤 沒有聽清楚 請再說一次
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.21,0:15:12.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊 那個…拍張照…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.84,0:15:12.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}錯誤
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.93,0:15:13.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}拍照…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.43,0:15:14.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}錯誤
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.78,0:15:16.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}您 您心情不好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.47,0:15:20.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你們兩個 來看看這個
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.46,0:15:21.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.58,0:15:22.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}水母果汁
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.20,0:15:26.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}姑且也算是這個嘉年華的名產果汁
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.52,0:15:28.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}無法想像什麼味道…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.44,0:15:30.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}什麼嘛 喝喝看不就知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.17,0:15:34.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊 安迪還是別喝比較…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.15,0:15:37.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯～ 真好喝
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.39,0:15:39.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}雖然是第一次喝 但味道還不賴呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.72,0:15:43.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}呃 是嗎 還不賴嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.86,0:15:46.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯～ 繪瑠不敢喝嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.67,0:15:48.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嘛…嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.80,0:15:50.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}咦 那個… 那個是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.60,0:15:51.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}要去看看嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.16,0:15:53.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}去吧 去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.66,0:15:56.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}來吧 艾拉也一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.14,0:15:58.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}小心點別走散囉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.86,0:16:08.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我… 又不是小孩子了 才不會走散…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.69,0:16:11.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}司 這個你也來喝喝看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.56,0:16:13.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}咦…但是這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.35,0:16:34.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.45,0:16:42.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}走散了…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.51,0:16:48.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}可惡 大叔再來一次
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.48,0:16:53.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}安迪好像很快樂呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.03,0:16:56.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}逛了不少地方呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.86,0:17:00.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}怎麼樣 你覺得她的記憶有恢復嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.24,0:17:05.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯 這就是現實
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.18,0:17:13.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我明年肯定不會再來這嘉年華了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.94,0:17:19.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}作為替代 我會和安迪一起去別的地方玩
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.54,0:17:24.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我不想安迪和奧利維亞共享記憶
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.57,0:17:27.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}而是希望創造出新的回憶
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.00,0:17:32.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不這樣的話 無論是對安迪還是奧利維亞都很失敬吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.85,0:17:34.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}繪瑠小姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.07,0:17:38.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}謝謝你今天陪我來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.66,0:17:41.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}多虧了你 我感覺甩掉了包袱
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.27,0:17:45.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不甩掉…不行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.60,0:17:53.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}吶 小司 能創造回憶的只有當下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.88,0:17:57.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}只能在這當下這須臾間去創造
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.64,0:18:01.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}當下這須臾間…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.17,0:18:10.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}煙火
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.87,0:18:13.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}咦 艾拉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.07,0:18:15.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}咦 難道是走散了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.82,0:18:16.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我去找找
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.85,0:18:30.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}振作起來啊 男孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.26,0:19:35.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}艾拉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.65,0:19:45.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}抱歉 讓你一個人在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.62,0:19:51.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你找到我了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.22,0:20:08.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}聲音真的很大吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.74,0:20:31.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那個…司
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.74,0:20:35.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}安迪的記憶沒有恢復吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.74,0:20:38.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你是怎麼知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.61,0:20:43.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我是不是讓司很痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.64,0:20:44.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}如果是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.79,0:20:45.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}希望你能夠說出來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.50,0:20:55.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我不想讓司因為和我搭檔而承受痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.58,0:21:07.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是很痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.11,0:21:09.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}非常非常痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.51,0:21:11.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}胸膛都要裂開了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.95,0:21:13.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就算如此
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.16,0:21:17.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我也想要一直做艾拉的搭檔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.90,0:21:20.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}為什麼要堅持到這種地步
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.88,0:21:22.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你還問為什麼 那種事肯定是因為
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.97,0:21:27.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是因為…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.38,0:21:36.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}因為 我喜歡艾拉
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.06,0:23:15.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}因為 我喜歡艾拉
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.40,0:23:25.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}說出口了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.01,0:23:27.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真有一手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.65,0:23:46.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不不不 不行
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.32,0:23:56.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}為 為什麼啊！！！！！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.38,0:23:58.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
